,"link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":924,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/07\/15\/do-not-prevent-masjid\/","url_meta":{"origin":25320,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Masajid: Do not stop women from attending Mosque","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 15, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said,\u00a0\u201cDo not prevent women from their share of the mosques if they seek your permission.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 900, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 442 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u00a0\u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":5837,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/02\/men-women-boast-majority\/","url_meta":{"origin":25320,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Jannah: Men and women boast over who is majority in Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 2, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Muhammad ibn Sirin reported: Some people were boasting, mentioning whether there would be more men or women in Paradise. Abu Huraira said: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, the first group to enter Paradise will have faces as bright as the full moon at\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25045,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/07\/11\/hijab-not-stare-at-women\/","url_meta":{"origin":25320,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Hijab: Men must respect women, not stare at them","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 11, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: Al-Fadl was riding with the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, and a woman from Khash\u2019am came. Al-Fadl began to stare at her and she stared at him. The Prophet made Al-Fadl turn his face in the other direction. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 1442, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":8094,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/13\/prophet-orders-rifq-nisa\/","url_meta":{"origin":25320,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Women: The Prophet orders gentleness with women","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 13, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, came to\u00a0some of his wives while they were being driven by a camel-driver named Anjasha. The Prophet said, \u201cO driver, be gentle when you carry the precious glass.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 5797, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2323 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062